(3, 2643, NULL, 'the-part-and-the-whole', 1, 1, 'The Part and the Whole', '2021-01-04', '2021-01-04', '00:00:00', '00:00:00', 0, '2021-01-04 03:00:00', '2021-01-04 03:00:00', 'America/Santiago', '<h4 class=\"has-text-align-justify\" style=\"text-align: center;\">This has been quite an exceptional year in almost all imaginable dimensions . As you know, the 2020 version had to be canceled. Now we cannot let the COVID19 pandemic jeopardize our tradition, so <strong>we decided to go for an online version!</strong></h4>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The 8th Afunalhue meeting <em>“La Parte y el Todo” (The Part and the Whole) – Advanced topics on high-energy physics and gravitation”</em>, will take place from the 4th to the 7th of January 2021.</strong></h3>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Downloadable version of the 2021 poster: <a href=\"https://laparteyeltodo.files.wordpress.com/2020/12/posterafunalhue2021.pdf\">PosterAfunalhue2021</a></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">This conference will be mostly devoted to the following topics:</h5>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Astroparticle physics.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Effective field theories.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Gravitation and cosmology.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Gauge theories.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Higgs physics.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Integrable systems.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lorentz symmetry violation.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">LHC physics.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mathematical physics.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Particle physics.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Quantum gravity and phenomenological implications.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">String theory.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Supersymmetry.</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Professors, undergrad- and grad-students, postdocs and foreign invitees are welcomed alike.</h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Students are highly encouraged to participate.</strong></h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The conference is free, but <a href=\"https://laparteyeltodo.wordpress.com/registration/\">registration</a> is mandatory.</strong></h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-left\" style=\"text-align: center;\">We encourage you to share the registration info with whom you see fit.</h4>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-left\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Registrations will be received until Dec 21st. Late registrations might be accepted but we must try to keep them to a minimum in order to get an estimate of the amount of participants with the necessary anticipation.</h4>', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2020-12-14 17:04:11', '2020-12-14 17:07:03', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'es_ES', 0);
